data.description: Wonderful well-maintained home in Carleton Falls with 4 Bedrooms and 3 1/2 Bathrooms - hard to find in this subdivision! Stainless Appliances, Quartz kitchen counters, Roof is 5 years old, mounted 70" UHD LG TV conveys, NEW AC (invoice provided upon request), annual pest control contract, gas fireplace recently serviced, NEW fenced backyard AND all NEW LVP flooring throughout the main level. Carleton Falls is 4.3 miles from Ft Eustis. Don't miss out on this opportunity! Pool and clubhouse included in HOA fee of $95 a month.
